Package ComparativeGenomics.FileHandling.DataHandling

Class XmapData

java.lang.Object
ComparativeGenomics.FileHandling.DataHandling.XmapData
public class XmapData extends Object
Stores the data for each individual alignment identified as the XMAP file. All of the aligned sites are stored as a Pair.
Author:
franpeters
